Class ProspectCustomerDTO

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.externalbank.otherbank.authentication.domain.dto.UserDTO
      • com.externalbank.otherbank.authentication.domain.dto.ProspectCustomerDTO
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public final class ProspectCustomerDTO
extends UserDTO
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class follows the Data Transfert Object design pattern. It is a client view of a ProspectCustomer. This class only transfers data from a distant service to a client.

    Isabelle Deligniere
